name: Token-maker
tagline: WPF Application for Creating Test Security Tokens

### Welcome to JWT/SAML Token Maker
Token Maker is a utility for generating security tokens. A .NET/C# WPF application.

### Authors and Contributors
Peter Bernhardt (@pbernhardt) and Trevel Beshore (@sfgadjo).
